{"type":"message","id":"2e2e2255","parentId":"f91d7b54","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:40:36.737Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ljni1c7mngqw_1","toolName":"feishu_wiki_space_node","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"node\": {\n    \"creator\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n    \"has_child\": true,\n    \"node_create_time\": \"1774591524\",\n    \"node_creator\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n    \"node_token\": \"JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg\",\n    \"node_type\": \"origin\",\n    \"obj_create_time\": \"1774591524\",\n    \"obj_edit_time\": \"1774592790\",\n    \"obj_token\": \"Rsm9dP1y7opy3zxaiBIcx0hEnJc\",\n    \"obj_type\": \"docx\",\n    \"origin_node_token\": \"JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg\",\n    \"origin_space_id\": \"7615846908665285857\",\n    \"owner\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n    \"parent_node_token\": \"\",\n    \"space_id\": \"7615846908665285857\",\n    \"title\": \"AI Coding\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"node":{"creator":"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9","has_child":true,"node_create_time":"1774591524","node_creator":"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9","node_token":"JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg","node_type":"origin","obj_create_time":"1774591524","obj_edit_time":"1774592790","obj_token":"Rsm9dP1y7opy3zxaiBIcx0hEnJc","obj_type":"docx","origin_node_token":"JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg","origin_space_id":"7615846908665285857","owner":"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9","parent_node_token":"","space_id":"7615846908665285857","title":"AI Coding"}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775659236728}}
{"type":"message","id":"44a49db4","parentId":"2e2e2255","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:42:12.354Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the report and write it to the wiki. I need to create a child node under the existing doc `JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg`.","thinkingSignature":"c7d7ea547a2f38fb4483430cef6672edd7a740c9b068aad9d8251c80f3616a29"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l55u07t5eg0i_1","name":"feishu_create_doc","arguments":{"markdown":"# 飞书插件个人授权机制实现原理\n\n> 本文档基于 OpenClaw 飞书插件源码分析，深度解析用户 OAuth 授权机制的设计与实现。\n\n---\n\n## 一、整体架构\n\n飞书插件的个人授权基于 **OAuth 2.0 Device Authorization Grant (RFC 8628)** 实现，称为 **Device Flow（设备授权流）**。整个授权体系由以下核心模块组成：\n\n| 模块 | 文件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `oauth.js` | 授权入口 | 发起 Device Flow、管理 pending 流程、身份校验 |\n| `device-flow.js` | 协议核心 | RFC 8628 实现：设备码请求 + Token 轮询 |\n| `token-store.js` | 凭证存储 | 跨平台安全存储 UAT（macOS Keychain / Linux AES-256-GCM） |\n| `uat-client.js` | 令牌管理 | UAT 自动刷新、并发锁防重放 |\n| `auto-auth.js` | 自动授权 | 工具层错误拦截 → 自动触发授权 |\n| `oauth-cards.js` | 授权卡片 | CardKit 交互式授权卡片渲染 |\n| `onboarding-auth.js` | 批量授权 | 引导新用户完成首次授权 |\n| `owner-policy.js` | 身份验证 | App Owner 身份校验（fail-close） |\n\n---\n\n## 二、OAuth 2.0 Device Flow 详解\n\n### 2.1 为什么用 Device Flow\n\n飞书插件运行在服务器端（无浏览器 UI），无法使用标准 Authorization Code Flow。Device Flow 允许：\n\n- 用户在**另一台设备**（如手机 App）扫码授权\n- 服务器端轮询等待授权完成\n- 全程无需用户在同一设备操作\n\n### 2.2 两阶段流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐          ┌─────────────────┐          ┌─────────────────┐\n│   OpenClaw      │          │   Feishu OAuth  │          │   用户手机      │\n│   (服务器端)    │          │   Server        │          │   (授权操作)    │\n└────────┬────────┘          └────────┬────────┘          └────────┬────────┘\n         │                            │                            │\n         │  1. POST /device_authorization                           │\n         │  (appId + appSecret + scope)                           │\n         │ ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────▶ │\n         │                            │                            │\n         │  ← { device_code, user_code, verification_uri_complete }│\n         │                            │                            │\n         │  2. 发送 CardKit 授权卡片   │                            │\n         │  (含 user_code + 链接)     │                            │\n         │ ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────▶ │\n         │                            │                            │\n         │  3. 后台轮询 /oauth/token  │                            │\n         │  (带着 device_code 每5秒)  │                            │\n         │ ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────▶ │\n         │                            │                            │\n         │                            │    4. 用户打开链接 → 授权  │\n         │                            │ ◀ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ │\n         │                            │                            │\n         │  ← { access_token, refresh_token }  (轮询到结果为止)    │\n         │                            │                            │\n         │  5. 存储 Token → 完成      │                            │\n```\n\n### 2.3 源码实现\n\n```python\n# ============================================================\n# Device Flow Python 实现（RFC 8628 标准）\n# ============================================================\nimport time\nimport base64\nimport json\nimport requests\nfrom urllib.parse import urlencode\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom typing import Optional\n\n@dataclass\nclass DeviceAuthResponse:\n    device_code: str\n    user_code: str\n    verification_uri: str\n    verification_uri_complete: str\n    expires_in: int        # 设备码有效期（秒），默认 300\n    interval: int           # 最小轮询间隔（秒），默认 5\n\n@dataclass\nclass TokenResponse:\n    access_token: str\n    refresh_token: str\n    token_type: str\n    expires_in: int\n    refresh_expires_in: int\n    scope: str\n\nclass FeishuDeviceFlow:\n    \"\"\"\n    飞书 OAuth 2.0 Device Authorization Grant (RFC 8628) 实现。\n    \n    参考源码: openclaw-lark/src/core/device-flow.js\n    \"\"\"\n\n    # 飞书 / Lark 平台 OAuth 端点\n    ENDPOINTS = {\n        \"feishu\": {\n            \"device_auth\": \"https://accounts.feishu.cn/oauth/v1/device_authorization\",\n            \"token\": \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/authen/v2/oauth/token\",\n        },\n        \"lark\": {\n            \"device_auth\": \"https://accounts.larksuite.com/oauth/v1/device_authorization\",\n            \"token\": \"https://open.larksuite.com/open-apis/authen/v2/oauth/token\",\n        },\n    }\n\n    def __init__(self, app_id: str, app_secret: str, brand: str = \"feishu\"):\n        self.app_id = app_id\n        self.app_secret = app_secret\n        self.brand = brand\n        self.endpoints = self.ENDPOINTS.get(brand, self.ENDPOINTS[\"feishu\"])\n\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    # Step 1: 请求设备授权码\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    def request_device_authorization(self, scopes: list[str]) -> DeviceAuthResponse:\n        \"\"\"\n        调用飞书 /device_authorization 端点，获取设备码和用户码。\n        \n        安全要点:\n        - 使用 HTTP Basic 认证 (appId:appSecret base64 编码)\n        - 自动追加 offline_access scope（获取 refresh_token 的前提）\n        - scope 参数为空时仅请求 offline_access\n        \"\"\"\n        scope_str = \" \".join(scopes) if scopes else \"\"\n        \n        # 强制追加 offline_access，确保能拿到 refresh_token\n        if \"offline_access\" not in scope_str:\n            scope_str = (scope_str + \" offline_access\").strip()\n\n        # HTTP Basic 认证\n        credentials = base64.b64encode(\n            f\"{self.app_id}:{self.app_secret}\".encode()\n        ).decode()\n\n        headers = {\n            \"Content-Type\": \"application/x-www-form-urlencoded\",\n            \"Authorization\": f\"Basic {credentials}\",\n        }\n        body = urlencode({\n            \"client_id\": self.app_id,\n            \"scope\": scope_str,\n        })\n\n        resp = requests.post(\n            self.endpoints[\"device_auth\"],\n            headers=headers,\n            data=body,\n            timeout=10,\n        )\n        data = resp.json()\n\n        if resp.status_code != 200 or \"error\" in data:\n            raise OAuthError(\n                data.get(\"error_description\") or data.get(\"error\") or \"Unknown error\"\n            )\n\n        return DeviceAuthResponse(\n            device_code=data[\"device_code\"],\n            user_code=data[\"user_code\"],\n            verification_uri=data[\"verification_uri\"],\n            verification_uri_complete=data.get(\n                \"verification_uri_complete\", data[\"verification_uri\"]\n            ),\n            expires_in=data.get(\"expires_in\", 300),\n            interval=data.get(\"interval\", 5),\n        )\n\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    # Step 2: 轮询获取 Token\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    def poll_token(\n        self,\n        device_code: str,\n        interval: int = 5,\n        expires_in: int = 300,\n        max_attempts: int = 200,\n        abort_event: Optional[object] = None,\n    ) -> TokenResponse:\n        \"\"\"\n        轮询 token 端点直到用户完成授权或设备码过期。\n        \n        关键状态处理:\n        - authorization_pending: 继续轮询（正常等待）\n        - slow_down: 增加间隔（服务端限流）  \n        - access_denied: 用户拒绝，终止\n        - expired_token: 设备码过期，终止\n        \n        参考源码: openclaw-lark/src/core/device-flow.js pollDeviceToken()\n        \"\"\"\n        deadline = time.time() + expires_in\n        attempt = 0\n        current_interval = interval\n\n        while (\n            time.time() < deadline\n            and attempt < max_attempts\n            and (abort_event is None or not abort_event.is_set())\n        ):\n            attempt += 1\n            \n            # 等待间隔（支持 AbortSignal 中断）\n            time.sleep(current_interval)\n\n            body = urlencode({\n                \"grant_type\": \"urn:ietf:params:oauth:grant-type:device_code\",\n                \"device_code\": device_code,\n                \"client_id\": self.app_id,\n                \"client_secret\": self.app_secret,\n            })\n            headers = {\"Content-Type\": \"application/x-www-form-urlencoded\"}\n\n            resp = requests.post(\n                self.endpoints[\"token\"],\n                headers=headers,\n                data=body,\n                timeout=10,\n            )\n            data = resp.json()\n\n            # 飞书返回格式: { code: 0 } 成功, { code: 非0 } 失败\n            code = data.get(\"code\")\n            error = data.get(\"error\")  # 标准 OAuth 格式\n\n            if code == 0 or error is None:\n                # 成功：返回完整 Token\n                return TokenResponse(\n                    access_token=data[\"access_token\"],\n                    refresh_token=data.get(\"refresh_token\", \"\"),\n                    token_type=data.get(\"token_type\", \"Bearer\"),\n                    expires_in=data.get(\"expires_in\", 7200),\n                    refresh_expires_in=data.get(\"refresh_token_expires_in\", 0),\n                    scope=data.get(\"scope\", \"\"),\n                )\n\n            # 仍需等待\n            if code == 1004012003 or error == \"authorization_pending\":\n                continue\n\n            # 服务端限流：自动增加间隔（最大 60 秒）\n            if code == 1004012004 or error == \"slow_down\":\n                current_interval = min(current_interval + 5, 60)\n                continue\n\n            # 终端错误\n            if error in (\"access_denied\", \"expired_token\"):\n                raise OAuthError(f\"Authorization failed: {error}\")\n            \n            # 其他错误：记录并继续（某些错误可恢复）\n            print(f\"[WARN] poll_token: code={code}, error={error}\")\n\n        raise OAuthError(\"Authorization timed out\")\n\n\nclass OAuthError(Exception):\n    \"\"\"OAuth 相关错误\"\"\"\n    pass\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、安全存储：Token Store\n\n### 3.1 跨平台存储策略\n\n| 操作系统 | 存储后端 | 安全机制 |\n|----------|----------|----------|\n| macOS | Keychain Access | 系统级加密，由 `security` CLI 管理 |\n| Linux | AES-256-GCM 加密文件 | XDG_DATA_HOME 目录，master.key 保护 |\n| Windows | AES-256-GCM 加密文件 | %LOCALAPPDATA% 目录 |\n\n### 3.2 存储结构\n\n```\n# 存储 Key（跨平台统一）\nService  = \"openclaw-feishu-uat\"\nAccount  = \"{appId}:{userOpenId}\"\nPassword = JSON(StoredUAToken)\n\n# StoredUAToken 结构\n{\n  \"userOpenId\": \"ou_xxx\",\n  \"appId\": \"cli_xxx\",\n  \"accessToken\": \"u_xxxx\",\n  \"refreshToken\": \"r_xxxx\",\n  \"expiresAt\": 1744142400000,     # Unix ms\n  \"refreshExpiresAt\": 1745174400000,\n  \"scope\": \"calendar:event:readonly wiki:node:readonly ...\",\n  \"grantedAt\": 1744056000000\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 Python 实现\n\n```python\nimport json\nimport os\nimport hashlib\nimport base64\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom cryptography.hazmat.primitives.ciphers.aead import AESGCM\n\nclass TokenStore:\n    \"\"\"\n    UAT 安全存储实现（Linux AES-256-GCM 版本）。\n    \n    参考源码: openclaw-lark/src/core/token-store.js\n    \n    存储路径: ${XDG_DATA_HOME:~/.local/share}/openclaw-feishu-uat/\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    DIR = Path(os.environ.get(\n        \"XDG_DATA_HOME\",\n        Path.home() / \".local\" / \"share\"\n    )) / \"openclaw-feishu-uat\"\n\n    MASTER_KEY_FILE = DIR / \"master.key\"\n\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n        self._master_key = self._load_or_create_master_key()\n\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    # Master Key 管理\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    def _load_or_create_master_key(self) -> bytes:\n        \"\"\"加载或生成 32 字节 AES-256 Master Key\"\"\"\n        if self.MASTER_KEY_FILE.exists():\n            return self.MASTER_KEY_FILE.read_bytes()\n        \n        import secrets\n        key = secrets.token_bytes(32)\n        self.MASTER_KEY_FILE.write_bytes(key)\n        os.chmod(self.MASTER_KEY_FILE, 0o600)  # 仅当前用户可读写\n        return key\n\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    # AES-256-GCM 加密 / 解密\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    def _encrypt(self, plaintext: bytes) -> bytes:\n        \"\"\"AES-256-GCM 加密，返回 iv || ciphertext || tag\"\"\"\n        import secrets\n        iv = secrets.token_bytes(12)  # GCM 推荐 12 字节 IV\n        aesgcm = AESGCM(self._master_key)\n        ciphertext = aesgcm.encrypt(iv, plaintext, None)\n        return iv + ciphertext  # IV 前置，tag 内嵌在 ciphertext 末尾\n\n    def _decrypt(self, data: bytes) -> bytes:\n        \"\"\"AES-256-GCM 解密\"\"\"\n        iv = data[:12]\n        ciphertext = data[12:]\n        aesgcm = AESGCM(self._master_key)\n        return aesgcm.decrypt(iv, ciphertext, None)\n\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    # Token CRUD\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    @staticmethod\n    def _account_key(app_id: str, user_open_id: str) -> str:\n        return f\"{app_id}:{user_open_id}\"\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def _safe_filename(account: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"文件名做 SHA256 哈希，避免特殊字符问题\"\"\"\n        h = hashlib.sha256(account.encode()).hexdigest()[:64]\n        return h\n\n    def save_token(self, app_id: str, user_open_id: str, token_data: dict):\n        \"\"\"保存 Token（自动加密）\"\"\"\n        account = self._account_key(app_id, user_open_id)\n        filepath = self.DIR / self._safe_filename(account)\n        plaintext = json.dumps(token_data, ensure_ascii=False).encode()\n        ciphertext = self._encrypt(plaintext)\n        filepath.write_bytes(ciphertext)\n        os.chmod(filepath, 0o600)\n\n    def get_token(self, app_id: str, user_open_id: str) -> Optional[dict]:\n        \"\"\"读取 Token（自动解密），返回 None 表示不存在或已过期\"\"\"\n        account = self._account_key(app_id, user_open_id)\n        filepath = self.DIR / self._safe_filename(account)\n        if not filepath.exists():\n            return None\n        ciphertext = filepath.read_bytes()\n        plaintext = self._decrypt(ciphertext)\n        return json.loads(plaintext.decode())\n\n    def remove_token(self, app_id: str, user_open_id: str):\n        \"\"\"删除 Token\"\"\"\n        account = self._account_key(app_id, user_open_id)\n        filepath = self.DIR / self._safe_filename(account)\n        if filepath.exists():\n            filepath.unlink()\n\n    def token_status(self, token_data: dict) -> str:\n        \"\"\"\n        判断 Token 状态:\n        - expired:    access_token 已过期\n        - expiring:   access_token 5 分钟内过期（需刷新）\n        - valid:      正常可用\n        \"\"\"\n        now_ms = time.time() * 1000\n        if now_ms >= token_data.get(\"expiresAt\", 0):\n            return \"expired\"\n        if now_ms >= token_data.get(\"expiresAt\", 0) - 5 * 60 * 1000:\n            return \"expiring\"\n        return \"valid\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、自动刷新：UAT Client\n\n### 4.1 刷新锁机制\n\n`refresh_token` 是**一次性使用**（用完服务端会颁发新的）。若并发请求同时触发刷新，第二个请求会用到已被消费的 refresh_token，导致失败。\n\n**解决方案：Per-User Refresh Lock**\n\n```python\nimport threading\nfrom collections import defaultdict\n\nclass UATClient:\n    \"\"\"\n    UAT 自动刷新客户端。\n    \n    参考源码: openclaw-lark/src/core/uat-client.js\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    # Per-User 并发锁：防止多个请求同时刷新同一用户的 token\n    _refresh_locks: dict[str, threading.Lock] = defaultdict(threading.Lock)\n\n    def __init__(self, app_id: str, app_secret: str, brand: str = \"feishu\"):\n        self.device_flow = FeishuDeviceFlow(app_id, app_secret, brand)\n        self.token_store = TokenStore()\n        self.app_id = app_id\n\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    # 获取有效 Token（自动刷新）\n    # ----------------------------------------------------------\n    def get_valid_access_token(self, user_open_id: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"\n        获取用户当前可用的 access_token。\n        - 若 Token 有效 → 直接返回\n        - 若 Token 即将过期（5 分钟窗口）→ 自动刷新\n        - 若 Token 过期且无法刷新 → 抛出 NeedAuthorizationError\n        \"\"\"\n        token_data = self.token_store.get_token(self.app_id, user_open_id)\n        \n        if token_data is None:\n            raise NeedAuthorizationError(user_open_id)\n\n        status = self.token_store.token_status(token_data)\n        \n        if status == \"valid\":\n            return token_data[\"accessToken\"]\n        \n        if status == \"expiring\":\n            # 主动刷新（加锁防并发）\n            lock = self._refresh_locks[user_open_id]\n            with lock:\n                # Double-check：可能在锁内被其他线程刷新了\n                token_data = self.token_store.get_token(self.app_id, user_open_id)\n                if self.token_store.token_status(token_data) != \"valid\":\n                    token_data = self._do_refresh(token_data)\n                    self.token_store.save_token(self.app_id, user_open_id, token_data)\n            return token_data[\"accessToken\"]\n        \n        # expired → 尝试用 refresh_token 刷新\n        lock = self._refresh_locks[user_open_id]\n        with lock:\n            token_data = self._do_refresh(token_data)\n            self.token_store.save_token(self.app_id, user_open_id, token_data)\n        return token_data[\"accessToken\"]\n\n    def _do_refresh(self, stored_token: dict) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"执行 refresh_token 刷新\"\"\"\n        if time.time() * 1000 >= stored_token.get(\"refreshExpiresAt\", 0):\n            # refresh_token 也过期了，无法刷新，需要重新授权\n            self.token_store.remove_token(self.app_id, stored_token[\"appId\"], stored_token[\"userOpenId\"])\n            raise NeedAuthorizationError(stored_token[\"userOpenId\"])\n\n        endpoint = self.device_flow.endpoints[\"token\"]\n        resp = requests.post(endpoint, data=urlencode({\n            \"grant_type\": \"refresh_token\",\n            \"refresh_token\": stored_token[\"refreshToken\"],\n            \"client_id\": self.app_id,\n            \"client_secret\": self.device_flow.app_secret,\n        }), headers={\"Content-Type\": \"application/x-www-form-urlencoded\"})\n        \n        data = resp.json()\n        \n        # 飞书: code=0 成功，其他失败\n        if data.get(\"code\") and data[\"code\"] != 0:\n            # 令牌被吊销或失效，清除后要求重新授权\n            self.token_store.remove_token(\n                stored_token[\"appId\"], stored_token[\"userOpenId\"]\n            )\n            raise NeedAuthorizationError(stored_token[\"userOpenId\"])\n\n        return {\n            **stored_token,\n            \"accessToken\": data[\"access_token\"],\n            \"refreshToken\": data.get(\"refresh_token\", stored_token[\"refreshToken\"]),\n            \"expiresAt\": time.time() * 1000 + data.get(\"expires_in\", 7200) * 1000,\n            \"refreshExpiresAt\": (\n                time.time() * 1000 + data[\"refresh_token_expires_in\"] * 1000\n                if data.get(\"refresh_token_expires_in\")\n                else stored_token[\"refreshExpiresAt\"]\n            ),\n        }\n\n\nclass NeedAuthorizationError(Exception):\n    \"\"\"需要用户重新授权\"\"\"\n    def __init__(self, user_open_id: str):\n        self.user_open_id = user_open_id\n        super().__init__(f\"User {user_open_id} needs re-authorization\")\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、工具层自动授权：Auto-Auth\n\n### 5.1 核心设计思想\n\n**不要让 AI 判断是否需要授权，而是让代码自动处理。**\n\n当工具调用遇到以下错误时，`auto-auth.js` 在工具层自动拦截并处理：\n\n| 错误类型 | 含义 | 处理方式 |\n|----------|------|----------|\n| `UserAuthRequiredError` | 用户未授权 | 直接发起 OAuth Device Flow |\n| `UserScopeInsufficientError` | Token scope 不足 | 用缺失 scope 发起增量授权 |\n| `AppScopeMissingError` | 应用未开通权限 | 发送引导卡片 → 用户确认 → 再发 OAuth |\n| `AppScopeCheckFailedError` | 应用权限检查失败 | 回退，不触发自动授权 |\n\n### 5.2 防抖合并机制\n\n同一消息中多个工具可能同时需要授权，如果每个都发一张卡片会导致骚扰用户。\n\n**解决方案：Debounce Buffer**\n\n```\n消息到达 → 工具A需要scope1 → 进入 debounce 队列（150ms 窗口）\n                    ↓\n            150ms 内工具B也需scope2 → 合并到同一队列\n                    ↓\n            150ms 到期 → 一次性发起 OAuth，scope 合并\n```\n\n### 5.3 App Auth → User Auth 接力\n\n当应用权限缺失时，引导卡片让用户去开放平台开通。**用户点击\"已完成\"后**，插件自动接力发起用户授权，两个流程无缝衔接：\n\n```python\n# Python 伪代码：卡片回调后的接力逻辑\nasync def on_app_auth_done(operation_id: str):\n    \"\"\"\n    用户点击应用权限引导卡片的\"已完成\"按钮后触发。\n    \n    1. 清除应用 scope 缓存（确保重新检查）\n    2. 验证应用权限确实已开通\n    3. 合并所有待授权的 user scope\n    4. 一次性发起 Device Flow\n    \"\"\"\n    # Step 1: 清除缓存\n    invalidate_app_scope_cache(app_id)\n    \n    # Step 2: 重新检查（确认真的开通了）\n    granted = await get_app_granted_scopes(app_id, token_type=\"user\")\n    \n    # Step 3: 合并 scope（应用缺失的 + 用户待授权的）\n    all_scopes = list(deferred_user_scopes) + list(app_missing_scopes)\n    \n    # Step 4: 接力发起 OAuth\n    await execute_authorize(sender_open_id, scope=all_scopes)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、Owner 身份校验\n\n### 6.1 为什么要 Owner 校验\n\n飞书应用默认允许企业内所有成员使用。但 OpenClaw 可以配置为**仅限 App Owner** 使用，防止滥用。\n\n### 6.2 实现机制\n\n```python\nimport requests\n\nclass OwnerPolicy:\n    \"\"\"\n    App Owner 身份校验（fail-close 策略）。\n    \n    参考源码: openclaw-lark/src/core/owner-policy.js\n    \"\"\"\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def assert_owner_access_strict(\n        app_id: str,\n        app_secret: str,\n        brand: str,\n        user_open_id: str,\n    ) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"\n        严格模式：仅 App Owner 可使用，否则直接拒绝。\n        若无法确定 Owner → 拒绝访问（fail-close，安全优先）\n        \"\"\"\n        # 1. 获取 App Owner 的 open_id\n        owner_open_id = await OwnerPolicy._get_app_owner(\n            app_id, app_secret, brand\n        )\n        \n        # 2. 比较\n        if owner_open_id is None:\n            # 无法获取 Owner → fail-close（拒绝访问）\n            raise OwnerAccessDeniedError(user_open_id, None)\n        \n        if user_open_id != owner_open_id:\n            raise OwnerAccessDeniedError(user_open_id, owner_open_id)\n        \n        return True\n\n    @staticmethod\n    async def _get_app_owner(app_id, app_secret, brand) -> Optional[str]:\n        \"\"\"通过企业自建应用 API 获取 App Owner open_id\"\"\"\n        import base64\n        credentials = base64.b64encode(f\"{app_id}:{app_secret}\".encode()).decode()\n        \n        resp = requests.get(\n            f\"https://open.{brand}.cn/open-apis/application/v6/applications/{app_id}/app_usage/overview\",\n            headers={\"Authorization\": f\"Basic {credentials}\"},\n        )\n        data = resp.json()\n        return data.get(\"data\", {}).get(\"owner\", {}).get(\"open_id\")\n```\n\n---\n\n## 七、身份校验：防伪造攻击\n\n### 7.1 攻击场景\n\n群聊中，攻击者可以：\n1. 将授权卡片链接转发给受害者\n2. 受害者完成授权后，攻击者获取了授权码\n3. 攻击者将授权码绑定到自己身份\n\n### 7.2 防御措施\n\nDevice Flow 完成后，立即调用 `/authen/v1/user_info` API **验证授权人的 open_id**，与发起授权的用户 open_id 比对：\n\n```python\nasync def verify_token_identity(\n    access_token: str,\n    expected_open_id: str,\n    brand: str = \"feishu\",\n) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    用刚拿到的 UAT 调用 /authen/v1/user_info，\n    验证实际授权人是否与预期一致。\n    \n    若不一致 → Token 不存储，卡片显示\"身份不匹配\"错误。\n    \n    参考源码: openclaw-lark/src/tools/oauth.js verifyTokenIdentity()\n    \"\"\"\n    domain = \"https://open.larksuite.com\" if brand == \"lark\" else \"https://open.feishu.cn\"\n    resp = requests.get(\n        f\"{domain}/open-apis/authen/v1/user_info\",\n        headers={\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {access_token}\"},\n    )\n    data = resp.json()\n    \n    if data.get(\"code\") != 0:\n        return False\n    \n    actual_open_id = data.get(\"data\", {}).get(\"open_id\")\n    \n    if actual_open_id != expected_open_id:\n        print(f\"[WARN] Identity mismatch! expected={expected_open_id}, actual={actual_open_id}\")\n        return False\n    \n    return True\n```\n\n---\n\n## 八、完整授权流程时序图\n\n```\n用户触发工具调用\n        │\n        ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Tool Client (uat_client.js / callWithUAT)               │\n│  1. 从 TokenStore 读取 UAT                             │\n│  2. 检查 Token 状态                                     │\n│  3. 调用 Feishu API                                   │\n└────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                 │\n        ┌────────┴────────┐\n        ▼                 ▼\n   API 返回成功        API 返回错误\n   (正常返回)          (触发 auto-auth)\n                          │\n                          ▼\n              ┌────────────────────────┐\n              │ auto-auth.js           │\n              │ handleInvokeError...   │\n              │  ├── AppScopeMissing?  │──→ 发送应用权限引导卡片\n              │  ├── UserAuthRequired? │──→ enqueueAuthRequest\n              │  └── 其他错误?         │──→ 回退到 handleInvokeError\n              └───────────┬────────────┘\n                          │ debounce 150ms 后\n                          ▼\n              ┌────────────────────────┐\n              │ oauth.js / executeAuthorize │\n              │  1. Owner 身份校验     │\n              │  2. 检查已有 Token     │\n              │  3. 过滤未开通的 scope │\n              │  4. 请求 Device Code  │\n              │  5. 发送授权卡片       │\n              │  6. 启动轮询          │\n              └───────────┬────────────┘\n                          │ 卡片显示 user_code\n                          ▼\n              ┌────────────────────────┐\n              │ 用户打开授权链接        │\n              │ 输入 user_code         │\n              │ 在飞书 App 内确认授权   │\n              └───────────┬────────────┘\n                          │\n                          ▼\n              ┌────────────────────────┐\n              │ pollDeviceToken 返回    │\n              │  1. 身份校验（verify）  │\n              │  2. 存储 Token          │\n              │  3. 更新卡片为成功状态  │\n              │  4. 发送合成消息        │\n              │    \"我已完成授权...\"   │\n              └───────────┬────────────┘\n                          │\n                          ▼\n              ┌────────────────────────┐\n              │ AI 收到合成消息         │\n              │ 自动重试原工具调用      │\n              │ (with 有效 UAT)        │\n              └────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 九、关键设计原则\n\n| 原则 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **Fail-Close** | 无法确定 Owner 时默认拒绝访问 |\n| **身份零信任** | Device Flow 完成后必须验证实际授权人身份 |\n| **一次性 Token** | refresh_token 并发锁，防止 Token 重放 |\n| **渐进式授权** | 支持增量 scope 授权，不 revoke 旧 Token |\n| **静默刷新** | Token 过期前 5 分钟自动刷新，对工具调用透明 |\n| **防抖合并** | 同一消息多工具授权合并为一次卡片交互 |\n| **App→User 接力** | 应用权限开通后自动接力用户授权 |\n| **安全存储** | macOS Keychain / Linux AES-256-GCM，Token 不落磁盘明文 |\n\n---\n\n## 十、总结\n\n飞书插件的个人授权机制是一套**生产级 OAuth 实现**，在无浏览器环境下通过 Device Flow 完成了安全、可靠的用户身份验证。核心亮点包括：\n\n1. **RFC 8628 标准实现** — 设备码 + 轮询，适用于服务器端场景\n2. **多层安全防护** — Owner 校验、身份验证、加密存储\n3. **开发者友好** — 完全自动化的授权流程，AI 无需感知授权细节\n4. **容错健壮** — 防抖合并、自动重试、渐进式 scope 授权\n","title":"飞书插件个人授权机制实现原理","wiki_node":"JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":24212,"output":6650,"cacheRead":37026,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67888,"cost":{"input":0.014527199999999999,"output":0.01596,"cacheRead":0.0022215599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.032708759999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775659236735}}
