{"type":"message","id":"1ca9a61f","parentId":"551d63d0","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:42:26.600Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The document was created successfully. Let me provide the user with the result.","thinkingSignature":"c285bbad8ed66acc1a822fa0225c0d18b750cb7d53e270ea081893bb6bacc982"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 文档已生成并写入知识库 ✅\n\n📄 **文档信息**\n- **标题**：飞书插件个人授权机制实现原理\n- **链接**：https://www.feishu.cn/wiki/WrTywzkE7ixIwXkiCMUcrupfnaf\n- **位置**：AI知识库 → AI Coding 目录下\n\n---\n\n**报告涵盖内容：**\n\n1. **整体架构** — 8 大核心模块一览\n2. **OAuth 2.0 Device Flow** — RFC 8628 完整流程 + Python 伪代码实现\n3. **安全存储 Token Store** — macOS Keychain / Linux AES-256-GCM 加密方案 + Python 实现\n4. **自动刷新 UAT Client** — Per-User 刷新锁防并发重放\n5. **工具层自动授权 Auto-Auth** — 错误拦截 → 自动触发流程 + 防抖合并机制\n6. **Owner 身份校验** — fail-close 安全策略\n7. **防伪造攻击** — Device Flow 完成后 `/authen/v1/user_info` 身份验证\n8. **完整时序图** — 从触发到自动重试的全程链路\n9. **10 条关键设计原则** — 生产级 OAuth 最佳实践总结\n\n每段核心逻辑都附带了 Python 代码块实现，源自 `openclaw-lark/src` 目录下的 TypeScript 源码翻译。🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":30956,"output":321,"cacheRead":37026,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68303,"cost":{"input":0.0185736,"output":0.0007704,"cacheRead":0.0022215599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02156556}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775659337304}}
